      "acceptanceCriteria": "Not assessed at MRL 2; single pump specimen used for validation testing is acceptable.",
      "rationale": "At MRL 2, statistical characterization of test sample variability is not required. Validation testing was performed on a single manufactured specimen of the FDA generic pump. Not assessed per MRL 2 scoping."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
