    "actor": "https://uofa.net/synth/actor/morrison-credibility-assessment-team",
    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Six factors are appropriately scoped out at MRL 2. The CFD model demonstrates sufficient credibility to support identification of worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device. RH < 1 for all 5 operating points confirms acceptability relative to the predicate device. The assessment team notes that all validation simulations were completed nominally and that the single convergence stall observed during preliminary mesh sensitivity was resolved by mesh refinement. The overall credibility evidence supports acceptance of the model for the stated COU.",
